{"tid":1678250,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「27/10檢討」路障、路障、路障好重要","createTime":"2019-10-27T14:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T01:12:37.000Z","uid":15567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d424dda5c559ee0ccda0c965df96e4a7aafa158c","tid":1678250,"uid":15567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T14:34:22.000Z","msg":"班狗咁易衝車過嚟捉手足<br />\n就係因為大型路障不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地須把握黃金五分鐘<br />\n立即起路障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結界師assemble!<br />\n所有人唔好係路鳩hea，即刻搵所有可以阻到路面嘅離物全部擺晒落面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係所有雜物都要擺落路面！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但不需要防守</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路障係防狗突擊而唔係陣地守衛<br />\n<br />\n有路障先會保障到手足<br />\n但守路障只係等狗嚟捉<br />\n<br />\n歡迎加料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後願香港人武運昌隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9e9bbfe1c13bdab2e37fe66ce742fb6481dd53","tid":1678250,"uid":15567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:47:10.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"8451624b37dc6157568d3d002ce5ca2907e610c4","tid":1678250,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae24d277cb04ab4ba7448b2af4bb371f67864f0","tid":1678250,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T01:12:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}